rows.label: qst202403_msg0001
rows.name:
That Nopon Trade Guild ID should
be around here somewhere.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0002
rows.name:
Hey, look! Look at this!
I found a weird-shaped stone.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0022
rows.name:
Uh, did you forget what we
were looking for?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0023
rows.name: Uhh... Errr...

rows.label: qst202403_msg0024
rows.name:
We're looking for Noganga's
stolen Nopon Trade Guild ID.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0025
rows.name: That certainly sounds familiar...

rows.label: qst202403_msg0003
rows.name:
Intruders!
What you doing, craa?!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0004
rows.name:
We've been spotted!
Battle stations, everyone!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0005
rows.name: ...They're not attacking.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0006
rows.name:
What's going on?
Is it a trap of some kind?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0007
rows.name:
Kountess!
We find kountess, craa!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0008
rows.name: Kountess return!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0009
rows.name: Must tell King!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0010
rows.name:
But King already gone to
Avaritia, craa!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0011
rows.name: You right!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0012
rows.name:
But kountess returned!
Craa! Craa! Craa!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0013
rows.name: Craa! Craa! Craa!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0014
rows.name:
What's going on?
I'm not a Tirkin!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0015
rows.name:
Don't be silly, kountess!
We know you anywhere!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0016
rows.name: Kountess!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0017
rows.name:
W-wait just a second!
Stop squawking for a minute!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0018
rows.name: I have no idea what's going on here.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0019
rows.name:
Looks like they have Ibuki confused
for somebody else? I think?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0020
rows.name:
Seems to be it.
At any rate, we won't find that
Nopon Trade Guild ID like this.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0021
rows.name:
I feel bad for the Tirkin, but
we're going to have to quieten
them down the hard way.
